E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You're going to fix that, John boy.
~z~Okay so I'm a little pissed off and I've been a bit of a prick lately,
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~所以我现在有点暴躁，表现得像个混蛋。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~We got to keep business afloat or we're fucked.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~资金链断裂的话我们就完蛋了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~I don't know what I'd rather go back to, stints in the hole or group share cluster fucks in that place.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我都不知道哪种更好，坐大牢还是在那破地方组团悔过。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~I mean we, meaning all of us, would love some hole.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~不是。我们，我们所有人，都想来点娘们。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You should be more careful of your leader, Johnny.
~z~Maybe a broken rib and a hangover.
~z~I told you we should have got the bike.
~z~I thought we had a truce here?
~z~You know what we're talking about. Billy's bike.
~z~Come on. Let's get your fucking bike.
~z~Get back on the bike, Johnny. It ain't an order....yet.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~回到摩托上，Johnny。暂时不算是命令...

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Follow me back to the house, boys.
~z~Okay. I'll save my questions until I see the chapter. And you better have looked after my baby.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~好。见到帮会之后我再决定怪不怪你。我的宝贝最好是没出差错。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Had any contact with my dear old friends, the Angels of Death?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~最近有跟我们亲爱的老朋友死亡天使打过交道吗？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Back to the source, boys. That bar had better be stocked.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~回基地吧，弟兄们。希望酒窖里还有酒。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~I've been putting up with rehab skanks getting sex therapy for the last few months. I need something real.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~这几个月都只能找戒毒所的公交车做性治疗。我需要实战。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Stay in formation, Johnny. Get behind me.
~z~And that I would really like some,
~z~Chill out, man. I just hope when we decide to take a break, to slow down, that it's still an option on the table.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~冷静，兄弟。我只是希望哪天我们决定休息一下，想要放慢脚步了，还能选择以前的心态。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Come on Johnny. Let's just get his bike. Come on.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~算了，Johnny，去把他的车子拿来吧。算了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, you know best, Bill, you're the leader. You make these decisions,
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，你自己清楚，Bill。你才是老大，

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You know, John boy, it was kinda hard. Harder than you'd think.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~其实吧，阿强，里面不好过。比你想的苦。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You're tense, Johnny. Must have been stressful heading up the chapter while I was away.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~你太紧张了，Johnny。肯定是替我管理分会的时候压力太大了吧。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~That's not gonna go back to normal. Angus lost his legs for life.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~那是不可能恢复的，跟Angus断掉的腿一样。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Listen, Billy, they were pissed and they had a reason.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~听着，Billy，他们跟我们的矛盾是有原因的。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~With a nose the size of yours there wouldn't be much blow left for the other brothers anyway, John boy.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~不过有这么个大鼻子在，你吸一口弟兄们就没得吸了，阿强。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Everything I do is about The Lost. I don't exist without my brothers - without you.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我所做的一切都是为了失落帮。没有兄弟，没有你，就不会有我。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Lives were lost today. Can't say it wasn't worth it though.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~今天出了几条人命，但也不能说不值得。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Forgotten how to ride while I was inside, did you?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我进戒毒所以后你就不会骑车了是吧？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Why the fuck haven't you got it back for me, friend, brother?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~你丫怎么还没把车弄回来，朋友，兄弟？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~It's hard to be proud when you don't have a roof over your head. I can show you the books.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~家徒四壁的时候，想站你都站不住。书里就这么写的。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You haven't always got the information, brother. So shut up and behave.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~你也不是每次都清楚状况，兄弟。老实点闭嘴吧。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You know, I've been here since I got out of juvie.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~你也知道，出了少管所之后我就在失落帮了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Tell her I'm inside, getting all sorts of fucked up.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~告诉她我回来了，但现在身心俱疲。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~I've seen men die for their brothers and men rat their brothers out. And I know that this gang don't mean shit
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我见过有人为兄弟牺牲，也见过有人出卖兄弟。如果手下不服从他们的老大，

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~I'll just taxi you around on your little welcome back tour.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~都是你的决定。我只是在你的回归欢迎会上当个车夫。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~And you know what? Peace and prosperity be damned.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~你知道吗？去他妈的和平与繁荣。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You told me? You don't tell me shit, you little fuck.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~跟我说了？轮不到你指手划脚，小畜生。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~What moron let Billy Grey outta the joint?
~z~Don't forget about the ugly broads you'd take home.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~可别忘了你带回来的那些丑娘们。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Billy! How's it feel to be on the old bike, man?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，Billy！骑上原来这辆车的感受如何，兄弟？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~ah, the Angels of Death took it to their place in Northwood.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~啊，死亡天使把车开到他们在Northwood的地盘了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~If you're in The Lost for the good times only, fair weather weekends in the Carraways, then you ain't in The Lost.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~如果你加入失落帮只是为了同甘，不能接受共苦，那就不算失落帮的兄弟。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Good thing I'm not fragile, Johnny. Otherwise I'd break when you treat me like this.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~幸好我不是易碎品，Johnny。否则你这样我早碎了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Why don't you give her a call for me?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~要么你替我打个电话给她吧？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Bikes and brothers, Johnny. Bikes and brothers.
~z~All I'm saying is we were cool.
~z~Yeah, Jim? Something tells me fucking up Pretty Boy and killing them Deadbeats ain't enough for him.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~是吗，Jim？我倒觉得光是收拾靓仔一顿和宰掉几个死妈天使对他来说还不够。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well, I ain't too happy about it neither man - you wanna turn around and go back to the clubhouse?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~的确，这样我也不高兴，兄弟。你想现在调头回会所吗？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Thank you for sharing! And now what's it feel like to you, Jonathan?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~感谢你的分享！那现在是什么感觉，Jonathan？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Now, let's be clear, I keep getting caught because assholes like you
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我就直说了，我这么容易进去都是因为你这样的混蛋

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~No, I just want my bike back, that's what this is all about.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~不了，我只是想拿回车子，就这一个目的。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~All the money in the world isn't worth anything if you don't have your pride, my brother.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~不是站着挣来的钱等于没挣，我的兄弟。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me Terry. That's her call. It's a free country.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~关我屁事，Terry。她爱咋咋，这里是自由国家。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~I don't know where you've been living, pal. Us brothers are the only free people I see.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我们真的生活在同一个国家吗？这里好像只有我们几个兄弟是自由的。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Be smart? You be smart you fucking chump, you're ridiculous.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~放聪明点？你个傻逼才要放聪明点，笑死我了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~when he's close to getting a fifteen year stretch?
~z~You ain't gonna keep those good looks if you keep falling off your bike, John.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~老从车上摔下来的话，你的小白脸可就不保了，John。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, well, it's some tough love you're showing them.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~那好吧，看来你向我们展示的是严厉的爱了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Now, Pretty Boy's waking up without a face.
~z~I'm the leader of the chapter again, Johnny. And you're just another brother. Can you handle it?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~现在我回来当分会老大了，Johnny。你又回归普通弟兄了。你能接受吗？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Not everybody's shoulders are wide enough to bear the responsibility.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~这种责任确实不是谁都能担得起的。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Hold on. I'm thinking you could use the guiding hand of your president on this noble quest.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~等等。这次的重要任务你们可以听本会长指示。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Fuck me, Joe Jon's gonna be pissed.
~z~You didn't have to do that. He told you who had the bike.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~没必要那么狠的，他都告诉你车在哪儿了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~No wonder you keep getting caught then, Billy. You can't stay away from it.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~难怪你经常进去，Billy。你是搞基搞上瘾了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Because this one, my chapter, isn't big enough to have two people pulling it in different directions.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~因为这里，我的分会，容不下两个方向不同的领队。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Shit, John. You should have a drink. Your nerves must be shot.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，John。你还是去喝几杯吧，你的哪根神经肯定断了。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~We took a break from saying "fuck you" to everything and we made some deals that worked out.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~当时我们不再动不动就「操你妈」，成功做起了生意。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Like when your wife is screwing the neighbor. I'm gonna be up all night tuning her back to normal.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~感觉就像你老婆跟隔壁老王偷情，我得花一晚上才能把她调教好。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Let's get the fuck outta here. Back to the house, boys.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~赶紧出发吧。返回会所，弟兄们。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Peace and prosperity be damned my brother.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~去他妈的和平与繁荣，好兄弟。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~That guy, he's an exceptional human being, an example to us all.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~那家伙，他是杰出的人类，是我们的榜样。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Like I told you when you were in there,
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~你在里面的时候我就跟你说过了。
~z~这里是死亡天使的地盘，小子。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~You ain't gonna keep those good looks if you keep falling off your bike, John.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~老从车上摔下来的话，你的小白脸可就不保了，John。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~But get it out of your system.
~z~This'll teach you to screw with The Lost.
~z~Who's been hanging round the house? The usual mattress cover?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~会所最近有谁来过？还是那几个人？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~it's screw you, you get in our way, you're gonna get your teeth kicked in.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~是滚你妈的，敢跟我们对着干就要你好看。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Look at me, manage to avoid prison and I'm still ass to cock with a dude.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~看看我，就算免了牢狱之灾，还是得顶着爷们的菊花。

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Come on, brothers. Get me back to church.
~z~You been missing me all that time I spent sharing and caring in rehab?
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~我在戒毒所遭罪的时候你想不想我啊？

E1B1AUD.original: ~z~Back me up, brothers, we're heading for a drink.
E1B1AUD.translated: ~z~跟上我，弟兄们，回去喝庆功酒了。
